General.Name: Safeture AB
General.Description: Safeture AB (publ) operates as a software as a service (SaaS) company. It offers cloud-based platform for employee risk and crisis management fields. The company was formerly known as GWS Production AB (publ) and changed its name to Safeture AB (publ) in June 2019. Safeture AB (publ) was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Lund, Sweden.
